response.overview: In the dimly lit halls of an exclusive art auction, Kai Lee, a celebrated artist drowning in the shadows of his own vices, finds solace in the allure of free booze. Little does he know, his intoxicated sanctuary is about to shatter. In a surreal twist of fate, two enigmatic young women materialize, each bearing a haunting secret: they both claim to be his daughters. As the night unfolds, the tangled webs of Kai's past unravel, revealing a cryptic connection that threatens to consume him. Amidst the seductive glimmer of the auction house, a mysterious saga of identity, deception, and redemption begins, casting Kai into a labyrinth of unanswered questions and eerie uncertainties.
response.title: Daddy-O
